/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a bustling street in Beijing, China. The vantage point is high, providing a bird's eye view of the scene below. The street, lined with lush green trees and bushes, stretches out into the distance, flanked by buildings on both sides. Cars of various colors are scattered along the road, adding a vibrant touch to the otherwise serene setting. The sky above is a clear blue, with a smattering of clouds dotting the horizon. The image is taken from a low angle, making the viewer feel as if they are standing right there on the street, looking up at the towering buildings and the expansive sky. The overall composition of the image paints a vivid picture of a day in the life of this vibrant city.
